William Welsh (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Welsh_(actor) 0 William Welsh (February 9, 1870 – July 16, 1946) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 153 films between 1912 and 1936. He was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, and died in Los Angeles, California.
